1. *Jasno* je da je ona nevin. (It is clear that she is innocent.)
2. Ona je *jasno* odgovorila na pitanje. (She clearly answered the question.)
3. Ona je *jasno* objasnila svoj stav. (She clearly explained her stance.)
4. *Jasno* je da je njegov izbor pogrešan. (It is clear that his choice was wrong.)
5. On je *jasno* vidio da je nešto pogrešno. (He clearly saw that something was wrong.)